description: This common Plezier purrs with a rating of 18, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 18, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Box for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [18 Votes, Common]
